---
title: "Frequently Asked Questions"
title_he: "שאלות נפוצות"
description: "Common questions about our web design services and process"
description_he: "שאלות נפוצות על שירותי עיצוב האתרים והתהליך שלנו"
layout: "layouts/page.njk"
permalink: "/faq/"
---

<!-- FAQ Accordion Section - Enhanced with CMS Integration -->
<section id="faq" class="faq-section">
  <div class="container">
    <!-- English Content -->
    <div class="lang-content" data-lang="en">
      <div class="section__header">
        <h2 class="section__title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="section__subtitle">Get answers to common questions about our web design services</p>
      </div>
      
      {% if collections.faqItems.length > 0 %}
        <!-- FAQ Categories -->
        <div class="faq-categories">
          {% for category, items in collections.faqByCategory %}
            <div class="faq-category" data-category="{{ category | slug }}">
              <h3 class="faq-category__title">{{ category }}</h3>
              
              <div class="faq-list">
                {% for item in items %}
                  <div class="faq-item" data-faq-item>
                    <button class="faq-question" 
                            aria-expanded="false" 
                            aria-controls="faq-answer-{{ loop.index }}"
                            data-faq-toggle>
                      <span class="faq-question__text">{{ item.data.question }}</span>
                      <span class="faq-question__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
                    </button>
                    
                    <div class="faq-answer" 
                         id="faq-answer-{{ loop.index }}" 
                         aria-hidden="true"
                         data-faq-content>
                      <div class="faq-answer__content">
                        {{ item.data.answer | safe }}
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                {% endfor %}
              </div>
            </div>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      {% else %}
        <!-- Professional placeholder when no FAQ items exist -->
        <div class="faq-placeholder">
          <div class="faq-categories">
            <div class="faq-category">
              <h3 class="faq-category__title">Pricing & Timeline</h3>
              <div class="faq-list">
                <div class="faq-item faq-item--placeholder" data-faq-item>
                  <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" data-faq-toggle>
                    <span class="faq-question__text">How much does a professional website cost?</span>
                    <span class="faq-question__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
                  </button>
                  <div class="faq-answer" aria-hidden="true" data-faq-content>
                    <div class="faq-answer__content">
                      <p>Website costs vary based on your specific needs and requirements. We offer transparent pricing with packages starting from ₪3,000 for basic business websites. During our free consultation, we'll provide a detailed quote tailored to your project.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item faq-item--placeholder" data-faq-item>
                  <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" data-faq-toggle>
                    <span class="faq-question__text">How long does it take to build a website?</span>
                    <span class="faq-question__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
                  </button>
                  <div class="faq-answer" aria-hidden="true" data-faq-content>
                    <div class="faq-answer__content">
                      <p>Most business websites are completed within 2-4 weeks. The timeline depends on project complexity, content preparation, and feedback cycles. We'll provide a detailed project timeline during the planning phase.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-category">
              <h3 class="faq-category__title">Design Process</h3>
              <div class="faq-list">
                <div class="faq-item faq-item--placeholder" data-faq-item>
                  <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" data-faq-toggle>
                    <span class="faq-question__text">What's included in your web design service?</span>
                    <span class="faq-question__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
                  </button>
                  <div class="faq-answer" aria-hidden="true" data-faq-content>
                    <div class="faq-answer__content">
                      <p>Our comprehensive service includes custom design, mobile-responsive development, content management system, SEO optimization, security setup, and training. We handle everything from concept to launch.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item faq-item--placeholder" data-faq-item>
                  <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" data-faq-toggle>
                    <span class="faq-question__text">Can I update my website content myself?</span>
                    <span class="faq-question__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
                  </button>
                  <div class="faq-answer" aria-hidden="true" data-faq-content>
                    <div class="faq-answer__content">
                      <p>Absolutely! We build all websites with user-friendly content management systems and provide comprehensive training so you can easily update text, images, and other content without technical knowledge.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
      
      <!-- FAQ CTA -->
      <div class="faq-cta">
        <h3 class="faq-cta__title">Still Have Questions?</h3>
        <p class="faq-cta__description">
          Can't find the answer you're looking for? We're here to help with personalized advice for your specific project.
        </p>
        <div class="faq-cta__actions">
          <a href="#contact" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg" data-scroll-to="contact">
            Get Free Consultation
          </a>
          <a href="/faq/" class="btn btn--secondary btn--lg">
            View All FAQ
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Hebrew Content -->
    <div class="lang-content" data-lang="he">
      <div class="section__header">
        <h2 class="section__title">שאלות נפוצות</h2>
        <p class="section__subtitle">קבלו תשובות לשאלות נפוצות על שירותי עיצוב האתרים שלנו</p>
      </div>
      
      {% if collections.faqItems.length > 0 %}
        <!-- Hebrew FAQ Categories -->
        <div class="faq-categories">
          {% for category, items in collections.faqByCategory %}
            <div class="faq-category" data-category="{{ category | slug }}">
              <h3 class="faq-category__title">{{ category }}</h3>
              
              <div class="faq-list">
                {% for item in items %}
                  <div class="faq-item" data-faq-item>
                    <button class="faq-question" 
                            aria-expanded="false" 
                            aria-controls="faq-answer-he-{{ loop.index }}"
                            data-faq-toggle>
                      <span class="faq-question__text">{{ item.data.question_he or item.data.question }}</span>
                      <span class="faq-question__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
                    </button>
                    
                    <div class="faq-answer" 
                         id="faq-answer-he-{{ loop.index }}" 
                         aria-hidden="true"
                         data-faq-content>
                      <div class="faq-answer__content">
                        {{ item.data.answer_he or item.data.answer | safe }}
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                {% endfor %}
              </div>
            </div>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      {% else %}
        <!-- Hebrew placeholder content -->
        <div class="faq-placeholder">
          <div class="faq-categories">
            <div class="faq-category">
              <h3 class="faq-category__title">תמחור ולוח זמנים</h3>
              <div class="faq-list">
                <div class="faq-item faq-item--placeholder" data-faq-item>
                  <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" data-faq-toggle>
                    <span class="faq-question__text">כמה עולה אתר מקצועי?</span>
                    <span class="faq-question__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
                  </button>
                  <div class="faq-answer" aria-hidden="true" data-faq-content>
                    <div class="faq-answer__content">
                      <p>עלויות אתרים משתנות בהתאם לצרכים ולדרישות הספציפיות שלכם. אנחנו מציעים תמחור שקוף עם חבילות המתחילות מ-₪3,000 לאתרי עסקים בסיסיים. במהלך הייעוץ החינמי שלנו, נספק הצעת מחיר מפורטת המותאמת לפרויקט שלכם.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item faq-item--placeholder" data-faq-item>
                  <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" data-faq-toggle>
                    <span class="faq-question__text">כמה זמן לוקח לבנות אתר?</span>
                    <span class="faq-question__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
                  </button>
                  <div class="faq-answer" aria-hidden="true" data-faq-content>
                    <div class="faq-answer__content">
                      <p>רוב אתרי העסקים מושלמים תוך 2-4 שבועות. לוח הזמנים תלוי במורכבות הפרויקט, הכנת התוכן ומחזורי המשוב. נספק לוח זמנים מפורט לפרויקט במהלך שלב התכנון.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-category">
              <h3 class="faq-category__title">תהליך עיצוב</h3>
              <div class="faq-list">
                <div class="faq-item faq-item--placeholder" data-faq-item>
                  <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" data-faq-toggle>
                    <span class="faq-question__text">מה כלול בשירות עיצוב האתרים שלכם?</span>
                    <span class="faq-question__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
                  </button>
                  <div class="faq-answer" aria-hidden="true" data-faq-content>
                    <div class="faq-answer__content">
                      <p>השירות המקיף שלנו כולל עיצוב מותאם, פיתוח רספונסיבי לנייד, מערכת ניהול תוכן, אופטימיזציה לקידום, הגדרת אבטחה והדרכה. אנחנו מטפלים בהכל מרעיון ועד השקה.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item faq-item--placeholder" data-faq-item>
                  <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" data-faq-toggle>
                    <span class="faq-question__text">האם אוכל לעדכן את תוכן האתר בעצמי?</span>
                    <span class="faq-question__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
                  </button>
                  <div class="faq-answer" aria-hidden="true" data-faq-content>
                    <div class="faq-answer__content">
                      <p>בהחלט! אנחנו בונים את כל האתרים עם מערכות ניהול תוכן ידידותיות למשתמש ומספקים הדרכה מקיפה כדי שתוכלו לעדכן בקלות טקסט, תמונות ותוכן אחר ללא ידע טכני.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
      
      <!-- Hebrew FAQ CTA -->
      <div class="faq-cta">
        <h3 class="faq-cta__title">עדיין יש שאלות?</h3>
        <p class="faq-cta__description">
          לא מוצאים את התשובה שאתם מחפשים? אנחנו כאן לעזור עם ייעוץ אישי לפרויקט הספציפי שלכם.
        </p>
        <div class="faq-cta__actions">
          <a href="#contact" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg" data-scroll-to="contact">
            קבלו ייעוץ חינם
          </a>
          <a href="/faq/" class="btn btn--secondary btn--lg">
            צפו בכל השאלות הנפוצות
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>